The paper discusses the measurement of impact of scientific papers on specific societal groups using altmetrics based on Mendeley data. The paper is likely to belong to the sub-category of Digital Libraries (cs.DL) as it deals with bibliometrics and altmetrics. It may also belong to the sub-category of Social and Information Networks (cs.SI) as it discusses the impact of papers on specific societal groups. Information Retrieval (cs.IR) is another likely sub-category as the paper deals with measuring impact. Cybernetics (cs.CY) and Sound (cs.SD) are less likely sub-categories as they are not directly related to the topic of the paper.
